article.description: — Steve Settle III scored 19 points and Randall Brumant scored 16 points making all seven of shot attempts and Howard beat American 90-56 on Saturday.
article.headline: Howard hands American 7th-straight loss with 90-56 win
article.linkText: Howard hands American 7th-straight loss with 90-56 win
article.story: WASHINGTON -- — Steve Settle III scored 19 points and Randall Brumant scored 16 points making all seven of shot attempts and Howard beat American 90-56 on Saturday. In ending its two-game losing streak, the Bison built a 9-0 lead, extended it to 27-13 and went to intermission up 43-22. Tai Bibbs scored 14 points and Elijah Hawkins 11 for Howard (5-4). Matt Rogers scored 28 points on 12-for-16 shooting and Stacy Beckton Jr. scored 13 for American (2-7) which has lost seven straight. ------
